        <cdata>
          <text>&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Medal of Honor Act&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;This bill increases the monthly special pension for living Medal of Honor recipients from $1,619.34 to $8,333.33 and establishes a rate of $1,489.73 for the monthly special pension for surviving spouses of Medal of Honor recipients. Both amounts must be adjusted annually for inflation. &lt;/p&gt;</text>
        </cdata>
      </summary>
